SIMPLE: impending
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Impending
<hw>Im*pend"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Hanging over; overhanging;
suspended so as to menace; imminent; threatening.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An <qex>impending</qex> brow.</q>
<rj><qau>Hawthorne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And nodding Ilion waits th' <qex>impending</qex> fall.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Imminent; threatening. See
<er>Imminent</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Impenetrability</ent>⟦br⟧
